# unit/

Test suite using BATS framework. Contains unit tests for Intent commands, project configuration, migration, and treeindex functionality. Tests verify core CLI behavior, steel thread management, backlog integration, and configuration handling.

## Files

- `agent_commands.bats` -- Tests for intent claude subagents commands (install, list)
- `basic.bats` -- Infrastructure tests verifying test helper and executable setup
- `bl_commands.bats` -- Backlog command tests (list, create, board)
- `bootstrap.bats` -- Global config and bootstrap command tests
- `config.bats` -- PROJECT_ROOT detection and config.json loading tests
- `fileindex_commands.bats` -- File index command tests with checkbox states
- `global_commands.bats` -- Global commands that work without project context
- `help_commands.bats` -- Help system tests for command documentation
- `init_commands.bats` -- Project initialization tests
- `migration.bats` -- Backup and legacy structure migration tests
- `project_commands.bats` -- Steel thread, backlog, and task command tests
- `st_commands.bats` -- Steel thread CRUD and listing tests
- `task_commands.bats` -- Task creation and validation tests
- `treeindex_commands.bats` -- Treeindex generation and shadow directory tests
